data.meta_description:
959 likes, 35 comments - thearfoundation on August 30, 2022: "Happy 40th Birthday to our founder, Andy Roddick! 

After first picking up a tennis racket at nine years old, Andy knew what he was born to do. Over the years, his devotion to the sport built his self-esteem and gave him a sense of self-worth. Now he is devoted to helping all young people find the same passion and confidence through expanding their opportunities. 

Help us celebrate Andyâ€™s birthday by giving back through a one-time or monthly donation of $40 & help us exceed our goal of $4,000! Give at the link in our bio! #ARF40for40".
